{"tid":1654340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我並唔認為裝修HKDI可以達到洩憤以外嘅目的","createTime":"2019-10-14T14:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T04:21:12.000Z","uid":126782,"like":45,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5dcf6175c9201829a103ab8b69179990130dbdf9","tid":1654340,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"我雖然點都唔割 支持手足裝修 但我諗裝修來都無咩野用<br />\n<br />\n因為條片一定太關鍵 佢亦未必會留低<br />\n<br />\n就算無即時銷毀 都俾政府拎走左底片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由HKDI嘅反口同明顯嘅剪片失敗去睇<br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得HKDI嘅反應似係特登同你講條片好關鍵 <br />\n<br />\n但係我地無權力俾你知道真相 希望你可以搞大佢去迫政府交片<br />\n<br />\n同時 我又唔覺得政府在意HKDI 你成棟野炸左佢政府都唔會理"},{"pid":"0b184b91efc1b233ac0d0215a063a31a523529bf","tid":1654340,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"唉 陰公 講真話就要食負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇下幾時有人開始屈我係黑警或五毛"},{"pid":"64d567644ea6c0c657e025906c7692638fe5d8d9","tid":1654340,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"push 1/10"},{"pid":"1f70fe10c8fb30ea490e1b40e7f97f32db826c8a","tid":1654340,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"是<br />\nHkdi比狗威脅"},{"pid":"9056e9d23b9a6624f95237b9dcd7420187e42988","tid":1654340,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"班鳩層，讀書人既風骨去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbbcf71097879cfe75ec2838b7b0d0184d190ac","tid":1654340,"uid":126782,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"大家起我底就知我為左女義士嘅遇害都好憤慨<br />\n<br />\n我只係覺得洩憤係HKDI係幫唔到件事<br />\n<br />\n畢竟人就係洩完憤 就覺件事完左 自已有做到啲野"},{"pid":"215688f805ddae2b1a1073191d19ef02f37fd0f6","tid":1654340,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T